testing_and_mocking_in_r
========================================================
author:
date:
autosize: true

Goal
========================================================

 * Understand the use of mocking in tests

Problem
========================================================

 * You want to test all code
 * You want the tests to pass fast

Example
========================================================

```{r}
#' Do a complex calculation
#' @param x a value
#' @return a complex result
do_it <- function(x) {
  # Complex calculation here
}
```

Example
========================================================

```{r}
#' Do a complex simulation
#' @param filename name of the file
#' that contains the x
#' @return the results
do_it_from_file <- function(filename) {
  x <- read_x_from_file(filename)
  do_it(x)
}
```
